<li id="cite_note-Friedxxi-18">^ <a href="#cite_ref-Friedxxi_18-0" title=""><sup><i><b>a</b></i></sup></a> <a href="#cite_ref-Friedxxi_18-1" title=""><sup><i><b>b</b></i></sup></a> <cite style="font-style:normal" class="book" id="CITEREF.5B.5BSaul_Friedl.C3.A4nder.7CFriedl.C3.A4nder.2C_Saul.5D.5D2007"><a href="/wiki/Saul_Friedl%C3%A4nder" title="Saul Friedländer">Friedländer, Saul</a> (2007). <i>Nazi Germany and the Jews: The Years of Extermination</i>. London: HarperCollins. pp.&#160;p.xxi. <a href="/wiki/Special:BookSources/0060190434" class="internal">ISBN 0-06-019043-4</a>.</cite><span class="Z3988" title="ctx_ver=Z39.88-2004&amp;rft_val_fmt=info%3Aofi%2Ffmt%3Akev%3Amtx%3Abook&amp;rft.genre=book&amp;rft.btitle=Nazi+Germany+and+the+Jews%3A+The+Years+of+Extermination&amp;rft.aulast=%5B%5BSaul+Friedl%C3%A4nder%7CFriedl%C3%A4nder%2C+Saul%5D%5D&amp;rft.au=%5B%5BSaul+Friedl%C3%A4nder%7CFriedl%C3%A4nder%2C+Saul%5D%5D&amp;rft.date=2007&amp;rft.pages=pp.%26nbsp%3Bp.xxi&amp;rft.place=London&amp;rft.pub=HarperCollins&amp;rft.isbn=0-06-019043-4&amp;rfr_id=info:sid/en.wikipedia.org:The_Holocaust"><span style="display: none;">&#160;</span></span></li>
<li id="cite_note-BauerRethinking48-19"><b><a href="#cite_ref-BauerRethinking48_19-0" title="">^</a></b> <cite style="font-style:normal" class="book" id="CITEREF.5B.5BYehuda_Bauer.7CBauer.2C_Yehuda.5D.5D2002"><a href="/wiki/Yehuda_Bauer" title="Yehuda Bauer">Bauer, Yehuda</a> (2002). <i>Rethinking the Holocaust</i>. New Haven, Conn: Yale University Press. pp.&#160;p.48. <a href="/wiki/Special:BookSources/0300093004" class="internal">ISBN 0-300-09300-4</a>.</cite><span class="Z3988" title="ctx_ver=Z39.88-2004&amp;rft_val_fmt=info%3Aofi%2Ffmt%3Akev%3Amtx%3Abook&amp;rft.genre=book&amp;rft.btitle=Rethinking+the+Holocaust&amp;rft.aulast=%5B%5BYehuda+Bauer%7CBauer%2C+Yehuda%5D%5D&amp;rft.au=%5B%5BYehuda+Bauer%7CBauer%2C+Yehuda%5D%5D&amp;rft.date=2002&amp;rft.pages=pp.%26nbsp%3Bp.48&amp;rft.place=New+Haven%2C+Conn&amp;rft.pub=Yale+University+Press&amp;rft.isbn=0-300-09300-4&amp;rfr_id=info:sid/en.wikipedia.org:The_Holocaust"><span style="display: none;">&#160;</span></span></li>
